                    </p>
                    <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 mb-2">
                        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/N3tRFayqVtk" title="Video de Design Patterns" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                    </div>
                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/0201633612" class="btn btn-outline-success" target="_blank">Ver en Amazon</a>
